Executive Secretary of National Economic Empowerment Council (NEEC) Ms. Beng’i Issa has called on local government authorities to prioritize planning of economic empowerment initiatives their daily programmes . She made the call in Dar es Salaam yesterday when she met media representatives to thank all stakeholders who participated in this year’s NEEC Stakeholders Annual Forum held in Dodoma this month. “We remind all local government authorities to adhere to guidelines as per Prime Minister Kassim Majaliwa directive and valuation will be done in June next year,” said Ms Issa. She said all regions that have not yet completed formulating investment guide – Dar es Salaam, Iringa, Mbeya, Njombe, Rukwa Singida and Shinyanga - to hurry up and submit the reports to NEEC.